data.description: Must See!  Lots of space! Immaculate 5-bedroom, 3 full bath, 3 car garage home with many upgrades.   First floor MIL quarters with upstairs & downstairs laundry areas.  Spacious formal dining room, walk through butler's pantry, eat in kitchen area, oversized kitchen island. Versatile loft area. Large owner's suite with large walk-in closet.  Ample storage throughout.  Fully fenced large backyard, backed up to green space reserve area. Open floor plan, high ceilings, ceiling fans, upgraded lights, new backsplash, new tiled island kick wall, blinds throughout, window aprons, granite countertop, Landscaping added, stainless steel appliances, gas stove, dishwasher, refrigerator. Great location, minutes to Buckeye Lake, State Route 79 & I 70, easy commute to Intel, Columbus & surrounding areas
